```plantuml
@startuml Simon-0711_ta_lyrics_sentiment_classification
actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "FastAPI Backend" as Backend
participant "LyricsGenius API" as LyricsAPI
participant "Elasticsearch" as Elasticsearch
participant "CNN Model" as CNN

User -> Frontend: Enter song/artist details
Frontend -> Backend: Send API request with song/artist details
Backend -> Elasticsearch: Check if lyrics exist
Elasticsearch -> Backend: Return lyrics or null
alt Lyrics not in Elasticsearch
    Backend -> LyricsAPI: Request lyrics
    LyricsAPI -> Backend: Return lyrics
    Backend -> Elasticsearch: Store lyrics
end
Backend -> CNN: Classify sentiment of lyrics
CNN -> Backend: Return sentiment classification
Backend -> Elasticsearch: Query similar songs
Elasticsearch -> Backend: Return similar songs
Backend -> Frontend: Send sentiment and similar songs
Frontend -> User: Display sentiment and similar songs
@enduml
```